  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 18th level you have learned to utilize your Genjutsu to bend your foes to your will. Once per casting, when a creature would fail a saving throw against a Genjutsu you cast, you can choose to spend 2 <strong>Actualization Die</strong>. When you do, the affected creature can no longer remake saving throws for the jutsu's duration.</p><p>Once you use this feature twice you must complete a long rest before you can use it again.</p>",
